ism\n| publisher        = Rowman & Littlefield\n| year             = 2015\n| url              = https://books.google.com/?id=mFCbCgAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage\n| isbn             = 9781442250161\n| ref              = harv\n}}\n*{{Citation \n|last1             = Cameron\n|first1            = Euan\n|chapter           = Cultural and Sociopolitical Context of the Reformation\n|editor1-last      = S\u00e6b\u00f8\n|editor1-first     = Magne \n|editor2-last      = Brekelmans\n|editor2-first     = Christianus \n|editor3-last      = Haran\n|editor3-first     = Menahem \n|editor4-last      = Fishbane \n|editor4-first     = Michael A. \n|editor5-last      = Ska\n|editor5-first     = Jean Louis \n|editor6-last      = Machinist\n|editor6-first     = Peter \n|title             = Hebrew Bible, Old Testament: The History of Its Interpretation\n|publisher         = Vandenhoeck & Ruprecht\n|year              = 1996\n|url               = https://books.google.com/?id=OMlT-FViF40C&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage\n|isbn              = 9783525539828\n|ref               = harv\n}}\n*{{Cite book\n|last1             = Carrigan\n|first1            = Henry L.\n|chapter           = Virgin Birth\n|editor1-last      = Freedman \n|editor1-first     = David Noel \n|editor2-last      = Myers\n|editor2-first     = Allen C. \n|title             = Eerdmans Dictionary of the Bible\n|publisher         = Eerdmans\n|year              = 2000\n|url               = https://books.google.com/?id=qRtUqxkB7wkC&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage\n|isbn              = 9789053565032\n|ref               = harv\n}}\n*{{cite book\n| last1            = Collinge\n| first1           = William J.\n| title            = Historical Dictionary of Catholicism\n| publisher        = Scarecrow Press\n| year             = 2012\n| url              = https://books.google.com/?id=L8C3TKNdn5oC&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage\n| isbn             = 9780810879799\n| ref              = harv\n}}\n* {{Cite book\n| last             = Coyle\n|